        <item>
            <title>男子植入 Neuralink 脑机晶片一年，可用脑控制电脑打机捉棋</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/31/neuralink-user-one-year-can-now-use-brain-control-computer/life-tech/health/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=neuralink-user-one-year-can-now-use-brain-control-computer</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/31/neuralink-user-one-year-can-now-use-brain-control-computer/life-tech/health/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 05:05:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Neuralink]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300275</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美国神经科技公司 Neuralink 于 2024 年 1 月为首位人类受试者诺兰・阿博（Noland Arbaugh）植入脑机介面晶片。这位 30 岁男子因 8 年前潜水意外瘫痪，现可透过意念操控电脑。该技术由 Elon Musk 创办的公司研发，备受瞩目。诺兰冀望此经验能推动科技进步，惠及更多人。事件同时引发隐私及安全性的讨论。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/neuralinkbbcnews041s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/neuralinkbbcnews041s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/neuralinkbbcnews041s.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：YouTube</p><p>诺兰于 2016 年因潜水事故导致肩膀以下瘫痪，生活完全依赖他人。他于 2024 年 1 月接受 Neuralink 晶片植入手术，术后能以意念移动萤幕游标，甚至下棋和玩电子游戏。他向《BBC》表示，这项技术让他重拾部分自主，重现童年乐趣。惟专家提醒，技术仍需完善，例如诺兰曾因晶片与大脑连接问题一度失去控制，后经软件调整修复。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/6b5ae4a003dd11f09b36-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/6b5ae4a003dd11f09b36-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/6b5ae4a003dd11f09b36.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：BBC</p><p>Neuralink 并非市场上惟一提供脑机接口的公司。Synchron 公司推出 Stentrode 装置，透过颈静脉植入，毋须开颅，已有 10 人使用，其中一位患者更结合 Apple Vision Pro 实现虚拟旅行。《The Guardian》2025 年 2 月报道，Neuralink 已为第二及第三名受试者植入改良晶片，功能更强。Elon Musk 预测，未来 20 年或有数亿人使用此技术，市场潜力庞大。诺兰参与为期 6 年的研究，期满后晶片或移除或关闭，其前景未明。他冀望技术能助更多人恢复机能，并计划成为脑机介面社群代言人。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_17547"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NofS_CgLP3E?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="http://thenewslens.com/article/250649">TNL</a>、<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cewk49j7j1po">BBC</a>、<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/science/2025/feb/08/elon-musk-chip-paralysed-man-noland-arbaugh-chip-brain-neuralink">The Guardian</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
